  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "My--one of my brother-in-laws got a job in the headquarters of the Polish agency.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And it was really all the difference in the world.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We were free.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We were able to shop and get back to a little more normal life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And again, I-- we didn't go to school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Because we felt it's temporarily and thinking what is our next step.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Because of our brother-in-law who worked the headquarters, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he found out that orphans, Polish orphans, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] have to register and will leave Russia, to where, nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father decided-- no, this was only Polish, not Jews-- underline, Polish orphans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father decided to give me and my younger brother a Polish first name.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because second name didn't make a different, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Feit, they didn't know it's Polish or Jew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we manage to join the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This was the first camp, which started to be organized.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And some way or another, some kids pointed out on us that we are Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they told us we cannot go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But this was ongoing thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we joined a second run, which [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we succeeded.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] brought us to a port by trains.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] some of my brothers and sisters went after us, which was my oldest sister, Chana, my nephew, [INAUDIBLE], Miriam, Joe, and Isadore.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they took a chance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They thought maybe they'll be able to join us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They saw us going on the ship.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
